OL,6,GThe BBC's new promo, The Square-Eyed
OL,7,GBoy, speaks of something very special.
OL,9,FIt is not the mere quantity of media
OL,10,Fwhich a child consumes which matters
OL,11,F` it is the quality.
OL,13,FThis is a timeless value of public
OL,14,Fservice broadcasting and the
OL,15,Fprinciple applies equally to adults.
OL,17,FSpend a life consuming fast food,
OL,18,Fjunk TV and it is a life wasted.
OL,3,CShould kids TV get an afternoon slot
OL,4,Con BBC Two?
