OL,6,FBut is time spent consuming content
OL,7,Fwhich informs or stretches the
OL,8,Fimagination time wasted Of course it
OL,9,Fisn't.
OL,11,FRather it is about the overall role
OL,12,Fconsuming media plays in someone's
OL,13,Flife.
OL,15,FIf a child is dumped in front of the
OL,16,FTV merely as an electronic
OL,17,Fchildminder, then there is little
OL,18,Fbenefit and the potential for harm is
OL,19,Fobvious ` lack of socialisation can
OL,20,Fhave lifelong consequences and
OL,21,Finactivity adds to the risk of being
OL,22,Foverweight or obese.
OL,3,CShould kids TV get an afternoon slot
OL,4,Con BBC Two?
