OL,6,FBut if a good proportion of that
OL,7,Fcontent informs or stimulates in one
OL,8,Fway or another ` and where a
OL,9,Fresponsible parent ensures the off
OL,10,Fswitch is used and the child does
OL,11,Fplenty of other things too ` then
OL,12,Fwhat's the problem?
OL,14,FA wider view of the world. New
OL,15,Fhobbies and interests stimulated. The
OL,16,Fempathy which both drama and real
OL,17,Flife stories can bolster.
